{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕沈璧君被小公子挟持展开。沈璧君醒来发现被小公子控制，小公子对她有邪恶意图。萧十一郎突然出现，与小公子对峙。小公子假意顺从，实则暗藏杀机，最终将沈璧君抛给萧十一郎后逃走。萧十一郎将沈璧君带到破庙养伤，两人在破庙中相处，沈璧君对萧十一郎产生复杂情感。本章展现了萧十一郎的机智与正义，以及沈璧君的柔弱与坚强。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你怕什么？我又不会吃了你，还是乖乖躺着吧，别惹我生气，我若生了气，可不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "果然是个美人，不生气的时候固然美，生了气也很美，难怪有那么多男人会为你着迷了，连我都忍不住想抱抱你，亲亲你。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我……你敢！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不敢？我为什么不敢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "有些事，像你这样的女人是永远也不会明白，一个男人若是真想要一个女人时，他什么事都做得出。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "美，真美……不但脸美，身子也美，我若是男人，有了这样的女人，也会将别的女人放在一边了……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像你这样的女人，实在连我也舍不得杀你，却又不得不杀你，我若带你回去了，他眼中还会有我吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "像你这样的女人，实在连我也舍不得杀你，却又不得不杀你，我若让你活下去，别人怎么受得了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你还没有死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我又不是老鼠，被猫爪子抓一下怎么会死得了？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你不是老鼠，简直也不是人，我遇上了你，算我倒了八辈子的霉，好，你有本事就下来杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你连逃都不想逃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我全身上下都是法宝时，也被你逼得团团乱转，现在我所有的法宝都用光了，还有什么法子能逃得了？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你为什么不用沈璧君来要挟我？我若要杀你，你就先杀她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "沈璧君既不是你老婆，也不是你情人，我就算将她大卸八块，你也不会心疼的，我怎么能用她来要挟你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你至少总该试试？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "既然没有用，又何必试？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你难道真的已认命了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "遇上了萧十一郎，不认命又能怎样？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "不对不对不对，我无论怎么看你都不像是个会认命的人，我知道你一定又想玩什么花样？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在我还有什么花样好玩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "无论你想玩什么花样，却再也休想要我上当了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你难道不敢下来杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我用不着下去杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那么你到底想怎么样呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你先叫马车停下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在你还想要我怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "抱沈璧君下车。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "text": "一直向前走，莫要回头，走到前面那棵树下，将沈璧君放下来……我就在你后面，你最好少玩花样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "遵命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小公子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我已将这烫山芋抛给你了，你瞧着办吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "躺下去，不许乱动！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你若一定要动，不妨先看看你自己的腿，无论多美的人，若是缺了一条腿，也不会很好看了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我是我，你是你，我不想知道你是谁，你也用不着知道我是谁。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我……我怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "有些话你还是不问的好，问了反而徒增麻烦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "莫非是你救了我？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "像我这样的人，怎么配救你？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我也知道像你这样的千金小姐，在这种地方一定呆不住的，可是现在你的腿受了伤，也只好先委屈些，在这里养好伤再说。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "喝下去，我保证这碗汤绝没有毒药的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "快睡，就算要走，也得等到天亮……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    }
  ],
